title: Howmeh Rural District (Gonabad County)
text: Howmeh Rural District () is a <a href="Rural%20Districts%20of%20Iran">rural district</a> ("dehestan") in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Gonabad%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Gonabad%20County">Gonabad County</a>, <a href="Razavi%20Khorasan%20Province">Razavi Khorasan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 16,701, in 4,732 families. The rural district has 31 villages.
